27Connection::Connection(PortType portType, Node &node, PortIndex portIndex)
28 : _uid(QUuid::createUuid()), _outPortIndex(INVALID), _inPortIndex(INVALID), _connectionState()
29{
30 setNodeToPort(node, portType, portIndex);
31 setRequiredPort(oppositePort(portType));
32}
33Connection::Connection(Node &nodeIn, PortIndex portIndexIn, Node &nodeOut, PortIndex portIndexOut, TypeConverter typeConverter)
34 : _uid(QUuid::createUuid()), _outNode(&nodeOut), _inNode(&nodeIn), _outPortIndex(portIndexOut), _inPortIndex(portIndexIn),
35 _connectionState(), _converter(std::move(typeConverter))
36{
37 setNodeToPort(nodeIn, PortType::In, portIndexIn);
38 setNodeToPort(nodeOut, PortType::Out, portIndexOut);
39}
40Connection::~Connection()
41{
42 if (complete())
43 connectionMadeIncomplete(*this);
44 propagateEmptyData();
45 if (_inNode)
46 {
47 _inNode->nodeGraphicsObject().update();
48 }
49 if (_outNode)
50 {
51 _outNode->nodeGraphicsObject().update();
52 }
53}
54QJsonObject Connection::save() const
55{
56 QJsonObject connectionJson;
57 if (_inNode && _outNode)
58 {
59 connectionJson["in_id"] = _inNode->id().toString();
60 connectionJson["in_index"] = _inPortIndex;
61 connectionJson["out_id"] = _outNode->id().toString();
62 connectionJson["out_index"] = _outPortIndex;
63 if (_converter)
64 {
65 auto getTypeJson = [this](PortType type) {
66 QJsonObject typeJson;
67 auto nodeType = this->dataType(type);
68 typeJson["id"] = nodeType->id();
69 typeJson["name"] = nodeType->name();
70 return typeJson;
71 };
72 QJsonObject converterTypeJson;
73 converterTypeJson["in"] = getTypeJson(PortType::In);
74 converterTypeJson["out"] = getTypeJson(PortType::Out);
75 connectionJson["converter"] = converterTypeJson;
76 }
77 }
78 return connectionJson;
79}
80QUuid Connection::id() const
81{
82 return _uid;
83}
84bool Connection::complete() const
85{
86 return _inNode != nullptr && _outNode != nullptr;
87}
88void Connection::setRequiredPort(PortType dragging)
89{
90 _connectionState.setRequiredPort(dragging);
91 switch (dragging)
92 {
93 case PortType::Out:
94 _outNode = nullptr;
95 _outPortIndex = INVALID;
96 break;
97 case PortType::In:
98 _inNode = nullptr;
99 _inPortIndex = INVALID;
100 break;
101 default: break;
102 }
103}
104PortType Connection::requiredPort() const
105{
106 return _connectionState.requiredPort();
107}
108void Connection::setGraphicsObject(std::unique_ptr<ConnectionGraphicsObject> &&graphics)
109{
110 _connectionGraphicsObject = std::move(graphics);
111 // This function is only called when the ConnectionGraphicsObject
112 // is newly created. At this moment both end coordinates are (0, 0)
113 // in Connection G.O. coordinates. The position of the whole
114 // Connection G. O. in scene coordinate system is also (0, 0).
115 // By moving the whole object to the Node Port position
116 // we position both connection ends correctly.
117 if (requiredPort() != PortType::None)
118 {
119 PortType attachedPort = oppositePort(requiredPort());
120 PortIndex attachedPortIndex = getPortIndex(attachedPort);
121 auto node = getNode(attachedPort);
122 QTransform nodeSceneTransform = node->nodeGraphicsObject().sceneTransform();
123 QPointF pos = node->nodeGeometry().portScenePosition(attachedPortIndex, attachedPort, nodeSceneTransform);
124 _connectionGraphicsObject->setPos(pos);
125 }
126 _connectionGraphicsObject->move();
127}
128PortIndex Connection::getPortIndex(PortType portType) const
129{
130 PortIndex result = INVALID;
131 switch (portType)
132 {
133 case PortType::In: result = _inPortIndex; break;
134 case PortType::Out: result = _outPortIndex; break;
135 default: break;
136 }
137 return result;
138}
139void Connection::setNodeToPort(Node &node, PortType portType, PortIndex portIndex)
140{
141 bool wasIncomplete = !complete();
142 auto &nodeWeak = getNode(portType);
143 nodeWeak = &node;
144 if (portType == PortType::Out)
145 _outPortIndex = portIndex;
146 else
147 _inPortIndex = portIndex;
148 _connectionState.setNoRequiredPort();
149 updated(*this);
150 if (complete() && wasIncomplete)
151 {
152 connectionCompleted(*this);
153 }
154}
155void Connection::removeFromNodes() const
156{
157 if (_inNode)
158 _inNode->nodeState().eraseConnection(PortType::In, _inPortIndex, id());
159 if (_outNode)
160 _outNode->nodeState().eraseConnection(PortType::Out, _outPortIndex, id());
161}

182Node *Connection::getNode(PortType portType) const
183{
184 switch (portType)
185 {
186 case PortType::In: return _inNode; break;
187 case PortType::Out: return _outNode; break;
188 default:
189 // not possible
190 break;
191 }
192 return nullptr;
193}
194Node *&Connection::getNode(PortType portType)
195{
196 switch (portType)
197 {
198 case PortType::In: return _inNode; break;
199 case PortType::Out: return _outNode; break;
200 default:
201 // not possible
202 break;
203 }
204 Q_UNREACHABLE();
205}
206void Connection::clearNode(PortType portType)
207{
208 if (complete())
209 {
210 connectionMadeIncomplete(*this);
211 }
212 getNode(portType) = nullptr;
213 if (portType == PortType::In)
214 _inPortIndex = INVALID;
215 else
216 _outPortIndex = INVALID;
217}
218std::shared_ptr<NodeDataType> Connection::dataType(PortType portType) const
219{
220 if (_inNode && _outNode)
221 {
222 auto const &model = (portType == PortType::In) ? _inNode->nodeDataModel() : _outNode->nodeDataModel();
223 PortIndex index = (portType == PortType::In) ? _inPortIndex : _outPortIndex;
224 return model->dataType(portType, index);
225 }
226 else
227 {
228 Node *validNode;
229 PortIndex index = INVALID;
230 if ((validNode = _inNode))
231 {
232 index = _inPortIndex;
233 portType = PortType::In;
234 }
235 else if ((validNode = _outNode))
236 {
237 index = _outPortIndex;
238 portType = PortType::Out;
239 }
240 if (validNode)
241 {
242 auto const &model = validNode->nodeDataModel();
243 return model->dataType(portType, index);
244 }
245 }
246 Q_UNREACHABLE();
247}

256void Connection::propagateData() const

258 if (_inNode)

260 _inNode->propagateData(_inPortIndex);
261 }

263void Connection::propagateEmptyData() const
264{
265 propagateData();
266}
